{"surah_number":86,"arabic":"الطّارق","latin":"Aṭ-Ṭāriq","transliteration":"At-Tariq","translation":"Yang Datang Pada Malam Hari","total_ayat":17,"location":"Makkiyah","ayat":[{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":1,"arabic":"وَالسَّمَاۤءِ وَالطَّارِقِۙ ","kitabah":"وَالسَّمَاۤءِ وَالطَّارِقِۙ ","latin":"Was-samā'i waṭ-ṭāriq(i).","translation":"Demi langit dan yang datang pada malam hari."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":2,"arabic":"وَمَآ اَدْرٰىكَ مَا الطَّارِقُۙ ","kitabah":"وَمَآ اَدْرٰىكَ مَا الطَّارِقُۙ ","latin":"Wa mā adrāka maṭ-ṭāriq(u).","translation":"Tahukah kamu apakah yang datang pada malam hari itu?"},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":3,"arabic":"النَّجْمُ الثَّاقِبُۙ ","kitabah":"النَّجْمُ الثَّاقِبُۙ ","latin":"An-najmuṡ-ṡāqib(u).","translation":"(Itulah) bintang yang bersinar tajam."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":4,"arabic":"اِنْ كُلُّ نَفْسٍ لَّمَّا عَلَيْهَا حَافِظٌۗ ","kitabah":"اِنْ كُلُّ نَفْسٍ لَّمَّا عَلَيْهَا حَافِظٌۗ ","latin":"In kullu nafsil lammā ‘alaihā ḥāfiẓ(un).","translation":"Setiap orang pasti ada penjaganya."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":5,"arabic":"فَلْيَنْظُرِ الْاِنْسَانُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ ","kitabah":"فَلْيَنْظُرِ الْاِنْسَانُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ ","latin":"Falyanẓuril-insānu mimma khuliq(a).","translation":" Hendaklah manusia memperhatikan dari apa dia diciptakan."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":6,"arabic":"خُلِقَ مِنْ مَّاۤءٍ دَافِقٍۙ ","kitabah":"خُلِقَ مِنْ مَّاۤءٍ دَافِقٍۙ ","latin":"Khuliqa mim mā'in dāfiq(in).","translation":"Dia diciptakan dari air (mani) yang memancar,"},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":7,"arabic":"يَّخْرُجُ مِنْۢ بَيْنِ الصُّلْبِ وَالتَّرَاۤىِٕبِۗ ","kitabah":"يَّخْرُجُ مِنْۢ بَيْنِ الصُّلْبِ وَالتَّرَاۤىِٕبِۗ ","latin":"Yakhruju mim bainiṣ-ṣulbi wat-tarā'ib(i).","translation":"yang keluar dari antara tulang sulbi (punggung) dan tulang dada."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":8,"arabic":"اِنَّهٗ عَلٰى رَجْعِهٖ لَقَادِرٌۗ ","kitabah":"اِنَّهٗ عَلٰى رَجْعِهٖ لَقَادِرٌۗ ","latin":"Innahū ‘alā raj‘ihī laqādir(un).","translation":"Sesungguhnya Dia (Allah) benar-benar kuasa untuk mengembalikannya (hidup setelah mati)"},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":9,"arabic":"يَوْمَ تُبْلَى السَّرَاۤىِٕرُۙ ","kitabah":"يَوْمَ تُبْلَى السَّرَاۤىِٕرُۙ ","latin":"Yauma tublas-sarā'ir(u).","translation":"pada hari ditampakkan segala rahasia."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":10,"arabic":"فَمَا لَهٗ مِنْ قُوَّةٍ وَّلَا نَاصِرٍۗ ","kitabah":"فَمَا لَهٗ مِنْ قُوَّةٍ وَّلَا نَاصِرٍۗ ","latin":"Famā lahū min quwwatiw wa lā nāṣir(in).","translation":"Maka, baginya (manusia) tidak ada lagi kekuatan dan tidak (pula) ada penolong."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":11,"arabic":"وَالسَّمَاۤءِ ذَاتِ الرَّجْعِۙ ","kitabah":"وَالسَّمَاۤءِ ذَاتِ الرَّجْعِۙ ","latin":"Was-samā'i żātir-raj‘(i).","translation":"Demi langit yang mengandung hujan753)"},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":12,"arabic":"وَالْاَرْضِ ذَاتِ الصَّدْعِۙ ","kitabah":"وَالْاَرْضِ ذَاتِ الصَّدْعِۙ ","latin":"Wal-arḍi żātiṣ-ṣad‘(i).","translation":"dan bumi yang memiliki rekahan (tempat tumbuhnya pepohonan),"},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":13,"arabic":"اِنَّهٗ لَقَوْلٌ فَصْلٌۙ ","kitabah":"اِنَّهٗ لَقَوْلٌ فَصْلٌۙ ","latin":"Innahū laqaulun faṣl(un).","translation":"sesungguhnya (Al-Qur’an) itu benar-benar firman pemisah (antara yang hak dan yang batil)"},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":14,"arabic":"وَّمَا هُوَ بِالْهَزْلِۗ ","kitabah":"وَّمَا هُوَ بِالْهَزْلِۗ ","latin":"Wa mā huwa bil-hazl(i).","translation":"dan ia (Al-Qur’an) sama sekali bukan perkataan senda gurau."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":15,"arabic":"اِنَّهُمْ يَكِيْدُوْنَ كَيْدًاۙ ","kitabah":"اِنَّهُمْ يَكِيْدُوْنَ كَيْدًاۙ ","latin":"Innahum yakīdūna kaidā(n).","translation":"Sesungguhnya mereka (orang kafir) melakukan tipu daya."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":16,"arabic":"وَّاَكِيْدُ كَيْدًاۖ ","kitabah":"وَّاَكِيْدُ كَيْدًاۖ ","latin":"Wa akīdu kaidā(n).","translation":"Aku pun membalasnya dengan tipu daya."},{"surah_number":86,"ayat_number":17,"arabic":"فَمَهِّلِ الْكٰفِرِيْنَ اَمْهِلْهُمْ رُوَيْدًا ࣖ ","kitabah":"فَمَهِّلِ الْكٰفِرِيْنَ اَمْهِلْهُمْ رُوَيْدًا ࣖ ","latin":"Fa mahhilil-kāfirīna amhilhum ruwaidā(n).","translation":"Maka, tangguhkanlah orang-orang kafir itu. Biarkanlah mereka sejenak (bersenang-senang)."}]}